title: Austria Car Registrations
description: Car Registrations in Austria decreased to 21402 in October from 27500 in September of 2022. Car Registrations in Austria averaged 32297.48  from 1987 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 60813  in May of 1996 and a record low of 10468  in December of 1993. This page provides - Austria Car Registrations - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Statistics Austria
